ited States House of Representatives from Oklahoma]]\n[[Category:Native American members of the United States Congress]]\n[[Category:Native American politicians]]\n[[Category:Oklahoma Republicans]]\n[[Category:Oklahoma State Senators]]\n[[Category:People from Moore, Oklahoma]]\n[[Category:Politicians from Shreveport, Louisiana]]\n[[Category:Republican Party members of the United States House of Representatives]]\n[[Category:Secretaries of State of Oklahoma]]\n[[Category:University of Oklahoma alumni]]\n[[Category:Watson Fellows]]\n[[Category:Yale University alumni]]\n[[Category:21st-century American politicians]]"}]}}}}